page_description: Learn about model versions in Azure OpenAI.
chunk_title: What you need to know about Azure OpenAI model version upgrades
chunk_content: What you need to know about Azure OpenAI model version upgradesAs a customer of Azure OpenAI models, you might notice some changes in the model behavior and compatibility after a version upgrade.  These changes might affect your applications and workflows that rely on the models.  Here are some tips to help you prepare for version upgrades and minimize the impact:* Read what’s new and models to understand the changes and new features.* Read the documentation on model deployments and version upgrades to understand how to work with model versions.* Test your applications and workflows with the new model version after release.* Update your code and configuration to use the new features and capabilities of the new model version.
